data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"The framework is a restrained editorial seed, but this brief calls for modern productized roofing: light grey/white, clean sans display, material tiles, service accordions, and one strong photography-led hero. I’ll use a modern-minimal palette with charcoal action treatment and keep the seeded images as the visual backbone."}

