id: 244
event: agent
data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"Built `index.html` with the seeded roofing imagery, modern productized layout, phone/form quote path, LocalBusiness/RoofingContractor JSON-LD, local SEO basics, and no fake reviews, awards, licenses, addresses, emails, or exact claims. The self-check passed for the required content and design constraints.\n\n<artifact identifier=\"ridgeline-roof-co-home\" type=\"text/html\" title=\"RidgeLine Roof Co. Home Page\">\n<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>RidgeLine Roof Co. | Roofing Contractor Brisbane & Gold Coast</title>\n  <meta name=\"description\" content=\"RidgeLine Roof Co. helps Brisbane and Gold Coast homeowners request roof repairs, restorations, metal roofing, gutter repairs, and roof inspections.\" />\n  <meta name=\"review-provenance\" content=\"ai-reference-placeholder; replace with real Google or customer reviews before live\" />\n  <style>\n    :root {\n      --bg: oklch(98% 0.005 250);\n      --surface: oklch(100% 0 0);\n      --fg: oklch(20% 0.012 250);\n      --muted: oklch(48% 0.012 250);\n      --border: oklch(89% 0.007 250);\n      --accent: oklch(24% 0.012 250);\n\n      --accent-soft: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent) 8%, transparent);\n      --fg-soft: color-mix(in oklch, var(--fg) 5%, transparent);\n\n      --font-display: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Display', system-ui, sans-serif;\n      --font-body: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Text', 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;\n      --font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', 'SF Mono', ui-monospace, Menlo, monospace;\n\n      --fs-h1: clamp(44px, 6vw, 78px);\n      --fs-h2: clamp(30px, 4vw, 48px);\n      --fs-h3: 22px;\n      --fs-lead: 19px;\n      --fs-body: 16px;\n      --fs-meta: 13px;\n\n      --gap-xs: 8px;\n      --gap-sm: 12px;\n      --gap-md: 20px;\n      --gap-lg: 32px;\n      --gap-xl: 56px;\n      --gap-2xl: 96px;\n      --container: 1180px;\n      --gutter: 32px;\n\n      --radius: 8px;\n      --radius-lg: 12px;\n    }\n\n    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }\n    html { -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; scroll-behavior: smooth; }\n    body {\n      margin: 0;\n      background: var(--bg);\n      color: var(--fg);\n      font-family: var(--font-body);\n      font-size: var(--fs-body);\n      line-height: 1.55;\n      text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;\n      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n    }\n    img, svg { display: block; max-width: 100%; }\n    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }\n    button { font: inherit; cursor: pointer; }\n    p { text-wrap: pretty; }\n    h1, h2, h3, h4 { text-wrap: balance; font-family: var(--font-display); }\n\n    .container { max-width: var(--container); margin-inline: auto; padding-inline: var(--gutter); }\n    .section { padding-block: clamp(56px, 8vw, var(--gap-2xl)); }\n    .section + .section { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }\n    .stack { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }\n    .stack > * + * { margin-top: var(--gap-md); }\n    .row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--gap-md); }\n    .row-between { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: var(--gap-md); }\n    .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: var(--gap-lg); }\n    .grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: var(--gap-lg); }\n    .grid-4 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: var(--gap-md); }\n    .grid-2-1 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: var(--gap-xl); align-items: start; }\n    .grid-1-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr; gap: var(--gap-xl); align-items: start; }\n    @media (max-width: 920px) {\n      .grid-2, .grid-3, .grid-4, .grid-2-1, .grid-1-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n      .container { padding-inline: 22px; }\n    }\n\n    .h1, h1 { font-size: var(--fs-h1); line-height: 1.02; letter-spacing: 0; margin: 0; }\n    .h2, h2 { font-size: var(--fs-h2); line-height: 1.08; letter-spacing: 0; margin: 0; }\n    .h3, h3 { font-size: var(--fs-h3); font-weight: 650; line-height: 1.28; letter-spacing: 0; margin: 0; }\n    .lead { font-size: var(--fs-lead); line-height: 1.55; color: var(--muted); max-width: 60ch; margin: 0; }\n    .eyebrow {\n      font-family: var(--font-mono);\n      font-size: 12px;\n      letter-spacing: 0.08em;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      color: var(--muted);\n      margin: 0 0 var(--gap-md);\n    }\n    .meta { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--fs-meta); color: var(--muted); }\n    .num { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }\n\n    .topnav {\n      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 10;\n      background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--bg) 94%, transparent);\n      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n    }\n    .topnav-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding-block: 14px; }\n    .topnav .logo { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 19px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0; }\n    .topnav nav { display: flex; gap: var(--gap-lg); }\n    .topnav nav a { font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); }\n    .topnav nav a:hover { color: var(--fg); }\n    .nav-phone { display: inline-flex; }\n    @media (max-width: 820px) {\n      .topnav nav { display: none; }\n      .nav-phone { display: none; }\n    }\n\n    .btn {\n      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px;\n      min-height: 44px;\n      padding: 11px 20px;\n      border-radius: var(--radius);\n      border: 1px solid transparent;\n      font-size: 15px;\n      font-weight: 650;\n      letter-spacing: 0;\n      transition: transform 0.05s ease, background 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;\n    }\n    .btn:active { transform: translateY(1px); }\n    .btn-primary { background: var(--accent); color: var(--surface); border-color: var(--accent); }\n    .btn-primary:hover { background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent) 86%, var(--surface)); }\n    .btn-secondary { background: transparent; color: var(--fg); border-color: var(--border); }\n    .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--fg); }\n    .btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--fg); border-color: transparent; padding-inline: 8px; }\n    .btn-ghost:hover { color: var(--muted); }\n    .btn-arrow::after { content: '→'; transition: transform 0.15s ease; }\n    .btn-arrow:hover::after { transform: translateX(2px); }\n\n    .card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 28px; }\n    .card-flat { background: transparent; border: 0; padding: 0; }\n    .card-rule { background: transparent; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--fg); padding: 24px 0 0; border-radius: 0; }\n\n    .hero { padding-block: clamp(28px, 5vw, 64px) clamp(56px, 8vw, 104px); }\n    .hero-panel {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.9fr) minmax(0, 1.1fr);\n      gap: var(--gap-xl);\n      align-items: stretch;\n    }\n    .hero-copy { padding-block: clamp(28px, 6vw, 76px); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; }\n    .hero h1 { max-width: 11ch; margin-bottom: var(--gap-md); }\n    .hero .lead { margin-bottom: var(--gap-lg); }\n    .hero-cta { display: inline-flex; gap: var(--gap-sm); flex-wrap: wrap; }\n    .hero-media {\n      min-height: 560px;\n      border-radius: 20px;\n      overflow: hidden;\n      position: relative;\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      background: var(--surface);\n    }\n    .hero-media img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }\n    .hero-note {\n      position: absolute;\n      left: 22px;\n      right: 22px;\n      bottom: 22px;\n      background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 88%, transparent);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);\n      border-radius: 12px;\n      padding: 16px;\n    }\n    .hero-note strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 2px; }\n    .trust-strip {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);\n      gap: 1px;\n      background: var(--border);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 12px;\n      overflow: hidden;\n      margin-top: var(--gap-xl);\n    }\n    .trust-strip span {\n      min-height: 76px;\n      display: grid;\n      place-items: center;\n      text-align: center;\n      background: var(--surface);\n      color: var(--muted);\n      padding: 14px;\n      font-size: 13px;\n    }\n    @media (max-width: 920px) {\n      .hero-panel { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n      .hero h1 { max-width: 12ch; }\n      .hero-media { min-height: 420px; }\n      .trust-strip { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }\n    }\n\n    .feature .feature-mark {\n      width: 36px; height: 36px;\n      display: grid; place-items: center;\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 10px;\n      color: var(--fg);\n      margin-bottom: var(--gap-md);\n    }\n    .feature .feature-mark svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; }\n    .feature h3 { margin-bottom: 6px; }\n    .feature p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 15px; }\n\n    .material-card { overflow: hidden; padding: 0; }\n    .material-card img { width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 4 / 3; object-fit: cover; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }\n    .material-card div { padding: 20px; }\n    .material-card p { margin: 8px 0 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 15px; }\n\n    .service-image {\n      overflow: hidden;\n      padding: 0;\n      min-height: 100%;\n    }\n    .service-image img { width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 480px; object-fit: cover; }\n    .service-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 150px 1fr; gap: var(--gap-lg); padding: 22px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }\n    .service-row h3 { font-size: 20px; }\n    .service-row p { margin: 5px 0 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 15px; }\n    @media (max-width: 640px) { .service-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--gap-sm); } }\n\n    .process-step { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 22px; }\n    .process-step .num { color: var(--muted); display: block; margin-bottom: 14px; }\n    .process-step p { color: var(--muted); margin: 8px 0 0; }\n\n    .faq-row { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 20px 0; }\n    .faq-row h3 { font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 6px; }\n    .faq-row p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); }\n\n    .field { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }\n    .field label { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); }\n    .input, .textarea {\n      width: 100%;\n      padding: 11px 14px;\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: var(--radius);\n      background: var(--surface);\n      color: var(--fg);\n      font: inherit;\n      font-size: 15px;\n    }\n    .input:focus, .textarea:focus { outline: 2px solid var(--accent-soft); border-color: var(--accent); }\n    .textarea { min-height: 112px; resize: vertical; line-height: 1.55; }\n    .form-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--gap-md); }\n    @media (max-width: 640px) { .form-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }\n\n    .tag {\n      display: inline-flex; align-items: center;\n      padding: 4px 10px;\n      background: transparent;\n      color: var(--muted);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 999px;\n      font-size: 12px;\n    }\n    .wordmark {\n      font-family: var(--font-display);\n      font-size: clamp(54px, 13vw, 176px);\n      font-weight: 750;\n      line-height: 0.9;\n      letter-spacing: 0;\n      color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--fg) 11%, transparent);\n      white-space: nowrap;\n      overflow: hidden;\n    }\n    .pagefoot { padding-block: var(--gap-xl); color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }\n    .pagefoot .row-between { flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--gap-md); }\n  </style>\n  <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n    {\n      \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n      \"@type\": [\n        \"LocalBusiness\",\n        \"RoofingContractor\"\n      ],\n      \"name\": \"RidgeLine Roof Co.\",\n      \"telephone\": \"0400 000 000\",\n      \"areaServed\": [\n        \"Brisbane\",\n        \"Gold Coast\"\n      ],\n      \"address\": {\n        \"@type\": \"PostalAddress\",\n        \"streetAddress\": \"Service-area business; address supplied on request\",\n        \"addressLocality\": \"Brisbane\",\n        \"addressRegion\": \"QLD\",\n        \"addressCountry\": \"AU\"\n      },\n      \"url\": \"\",\n      \"sameAs\": [],\n      \"hasMap\": \"https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Brisbane+roofing+contractor\"\n    }\n  </script>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <header class=\"topnav\" data-od-id=\"topnav\">\n    <div class=\"container topnav-inner\">\n      <a class=\"logo\" href=\"#top\" aria-label=\"RidgeLine Roof Co. home\">RidgeLine Roof Co.</a>\n      <nav aria-label=\"Primary navigation\">\n        <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n        <a href=\"#materials\">Materials</a>\n        <a href=\"#process\">Process</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n      </nav>\n      <a class=\"btn btn-primary nav-phone\" href=\"tel:0400000000\">Call 0400 000 000</a>\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  <main id=\"content\">\n    <section class=\"section hero\" id=\"top\" data-od-id=\"hero\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"hero-panel\">\n          <div class=\"hero-copy\">\n            <p class=\"eyebrow\">Roof repairs · restoration · inspections</p>\n            <h1>Roofing for Brisbane and Gold Coast homes</h1>\n            <p class=\"lead\">RidgeLine Roof Co. helps homeowners request practical roof repairs, restorations, metal roofing, gutter repairs, and roof inspections with a clear quote path.</p>\n            <div class=\"hero-cta\">\n              <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"#contact\">Request an inspection</a>\n              <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"tel:0400000000\">Call 0400 000 000</a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"hero-media\">\n            <img src=\"assets/hero-family3-hero-modern-metal-roof-sunset-wide.png\" alt=\"Modern metal roof at sunset on a finished home\" />\n            <div class=\"hero-note\">\n              <strong>Clear scope before work begins</strong>\n              <span class=\"meta\">Inspection notes, repair options, and material recommendations are discussed before quoting.</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"trust-strip\" aria-label=\"Service highlights\">\n          <span>Roof repairs for leaks, storm damage, and wear</span>\n          <span>Restoration planning for tiled and metal roofs</span>\n          <span>Inspection-first advice before major work</span>\n          <span>Local coverage across Brisbane and Gold Coast</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" id=\"services\" data-od-id=\"services\">\n      <div class=\"container stack\" style=\"gap: 56px;\">\n        <div class=\"row-between\" style=\"align-items: end;\">\n          <div style=\"max-width: 44ch;\">\n            <p class=\"eyebrow\">Request the right work</p>\n            <h2>Roofing services presented in plain language.</h2>\n          </div>\n          <a class=\"btn btn-ghost btn-arrow\" href=\"#contact\">Ask for a quote</a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"grid-3\">\n          <div class=\"feature card-flat\">\n            <div class=\"feature-mark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\"><path d=\"M4 13l8-7 8 7\"/><path d=\"M6 12v7h12v-7\"/></svg>\n            </div>\n            <h3>Roof repairs</h3>\n            <p>Help with leaks, loose flashings, cracked bedding, storm wear, and smaller repairs that need a roofer's eye.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature card-flat\">\n            <div class=\"feature-mark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\"><path d=\"M4 17h16\"/><path d=\"M6 14l6-8 6 8\"/></svg>\n            </div>\n            <h3>Roof restoration</h3>\n            <p>Assessment-led restoration planning for tired tiled or metal roofs, including cleaning, repair scope, and finish options.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature card-flat\">\n            <div class=\"feature-mark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\"><path d=\"M4 8h16M4 12h16M4 16h16\"/></svg>\n            </div>\n            <h3>Metal roofing</h3>\n            <p>Modern metal roof work for homeowners comparing durable profiles, clean detailing, and a sharper exterior finish.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature card-flat\">\n            <div class=\"feature-mark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\"><path d=\"M5 7h14v6a5 5 0 0 1-5 5H9a4 4 0 0 1-4-4z\"/></svg>\n            </div>\n            <h3>Gutter repairs</h3>\n            <p>Repair and replacement advice for damaged, blocked, leaking, or poorly falling gutters around the roofline.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature card-flat\">\n            <div class=\"feature-mark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\"><circle cx=\"10\" cy=\"10\" r=\"5\"/><path d=\"M14 14l6 6\"/></svg>\n            </div>\n            <h3>Roof inspections</h3>\n            <p>A practical first step when you need a roofer to check condition, photograph issues, and explain the likely next move.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature card-flat\">\n            <div class=\"feature-mark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\"><path d=\"M5 19h14\"/><path d=\"M7 16l5-11 5 11\"/></svg>\n            </div>\n            <h3>Quote planning</h3>\n            <p>Simple request intake, site context, roof access notes, and a clear path from enquiry to inspection or quote.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" id=\"materials\" data-od-id=\"materials\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div style=\"max-width: 42ch; margin-bottom: 42px;\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Roof systems and finishes</p>\n          <h2>Compare the look before committing to the scope.</h2>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"grid-3\">\n          <article class=\"card material-card\">\n            <img src=\"assets/materialMetal-family3-product-standing-seam-metal-sample.png\" alt=\"Standing seam metal roofing material sample\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n            <div>\n              <h3>Standing seam metal</h3>\n              <p>Clean lines for contemporary homes and extensions where the roof is part of the architecture.</p>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"card material-card\">\n            <img src=\"assets/materialTerracotta-family3-product-terracotta-tile-sample.png\" alt=\"Terracotta roof tile material sample\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n            <div>\n              <h3>Terracotta tile</h3>\n              <p>A familiar Brisbane and Gold Coast finish when restoration needs to respect an existing tile profile.</p>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"card material-card\">\n            <img src=\"assets/materialComposite-family3-product-composite-shingle-sample.png\" alt=\"Composite roof shingle material sample\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n            <div>\n              <h3>Composite shingle</h3>\n              <p>A textured option for homeowners considering a refreshed roof face without a busy exterior treatment.</p>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"proof\">\n      <div class=\"container grid-1-2\">\n        <div class=\"card service-image\">\n          <img src=\"assets/service-family3-service-modern-roofer-metal-roof.png\" alt=\"Roofer working on a modern metal roof\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Concrete work cues</p>\n          <h2>Useful detail instead of vague promises.</h2>\n          <div style=\"margin-top: 34px;\">\n            <article class=\"service-row\">\n              <span class=\"meta\">Inspect</span>\n              <div>\n                <h3>Start with visible roof condition</h3>\n                <p>Leaks, flashing, gutters, bedding, corrosion, and access constraints are checked before a repair or restoration path is suggested.</p>\n              </div>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"service-row\">\n              <span class=\"meta\">Scope</span>\n              <div>\n                <h3>Separate urgent repairs from upgrades</h3>\n                <p>Homeowners can distinguish what needs attention now from larger finish, material, or restoration decisions.</p>\n              </div>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"service-row\">\n              <span class=\"meta\">Explain</span>\n              <div>\n                <h3>Make the quote easier to compare</h3>\n                <p>The enquiry flow captures roof type, known issues, timing, and photos where available, so the conversation starts with useful context.</p>\n              </div>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" id=\"process\" data-od-id=\"quote-process\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"grid-2\" style=\"align-items: end; margin-bottom: 46px;\">\n          <div>\n            <p class=\"eyebrow\">Inspection to quote</p>\n            <h2>A simple path for roof work that needs a closer look.</h2>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"lead\">Call the team or send a short enquiry. RidgeLine Roof Co. will use the details to discuss next steps for inspection, repair scope, or quote preparation.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"grid-4\">\n          <article class=\"process-step\">\n            <span class=\"num\">01</span>\n            <h3>Describe the roof</h3>\n            <p>Share roof type, suburb, visible issue, and whether the request is urgent.</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"process-step\">\n            <span class=\"num\">02</span>\n            <h3>Attach photos if useful</h3>\n            <p>Photos can help identify gutters, flashing, corrosion, broken tiles, or access concerns.</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"process-step\">\n            <span class=\"num\">03</span>\n            <h3>Book the next step</h3>\n            <p>The team confirms whether an inspection, repair visit, or quote conversation is the right next move.</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"process-step\">\n            <span class=\"num\">04</span>\n            <h3>Review the scope</h3>\n            <p>Discuss practical work options before committing to repair, restoration, or metal roofing work.</p>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" id=\"contact\" data-od-id=\"faq-contact-footer\">\n      <div class=\"container grid-2\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Questions homeowners ask</p>\n          <h2>Before you request a roof inspection.</h2>\n          <div style=\"margin-top: 34px;\">\n            <article class=\"faq-row\">\n              <h3>Can you quote from photos?</h3>\n              <p>Photos are useful for context, but roof work often needs site-specific inspection before final scope is confirmed.</p>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"faq-row\">\n              <h3>Do you handle both tiled and metal roofs?</h3>\n              <p>Yes. Enquiries can cover repairs, restoration planning, gutter issues, and modern metal roofing work.</p>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"faq-row\">\n              <h3>What service areas are covered?</h3>\n              <p>RidgeLine Roof Co. serves Brisbane and Gold Coast homeowners.</p>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"faq-row\">\n              <h3>What should I include in the form?</h3>\n              <p>Your suburb, roof type if known, issue description, preferred timing, and whether water is entering the home.</p>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"row\" style=\"flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 26px;\">\n            <span class=\"tag\">Brisbane</span>\n            <span class=\"tag\">Gold Coast</span>\n            <span class=\"tag\">Roof repairs</span>\n            <span class=\"tag\">Inspections</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <aside class=\"card\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Request a quote</p>\n          <h2 style=\"font-size: clamp(28px, 3vw, 38px);\">Tell us what is happening on the roof.</h2>\n          <form style=\"margin-top: 28px;\" action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n            <div class=\"form-grid\">\n              <div class=\"field\">\n                <label for=\"name\">Name</label>\n                <input class=\"input\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" autocomplete=\"name\" />\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"field\">\n                <label for=\"phone\">Phone</label>\n                <input class=\"input\" id=\"phone\" name=\"phone\" autocomplete=\"tel\" />\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"field\" style=\"margin-top: 16px;\">\n              <label for=\"suburb\">Suburb</label>\n              <input class=\"input\" id=\"suburb\" name=\"suburb\" autocomplete=\"address-level2\" />\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"field\" style=\"margin-top: 16px;\">\n              <label for=\"service\">What do you need?</label>\n              <select class=\"input\" id=\"service\" name=\"service\">\n                <option>Roof inspection</option>\n                <option>Roof repairs</option>\n                <option>Roof restoration</option>\n                <option>Metal roofing</option>\n                <option>Gutter repairs</option>\n              </select>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"field\" style=\"margin-top: 16px;\">\n              <label for=\"message\">Roof details</label>\n              <textarea class=\"textarea\" id=\"message\" name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Tell us what you can see, when it started, and whether it is urgent.\"></textarea>\n            </div>\n            <button class=\"btn btn-primary\" type=\"submit\" style=\"width: 100%; margin-top: 18px;\">Send enquiry</button>\n          </form>\n          <hr class=\"rule\" style=\"margin: 24px 0;\" />\n          <p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px; color: var(--muted);\">Prefer to talk?</p>\n          <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"tel:0400000000\" style=\"width: 100%;\">Call 0400 000 000</a>\n          <p class=\"meta\" style=\"margin: 18px 0 0;\">Hours: by enquiry. Directions: <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Brisbane+roofing+contractor\">Brisbane roofing contractor</a>.</p>\n        </aside>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  </main>\n\n  <footer class=\"pagefoot\" data-od-id=\"footer\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"wordmark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">RidgeLine</div>\n      <div class=\"row-between\" style=\"margin-top: 28px;\">\n        <span>© RidgeLine Roof Co. · Roofing contractor for Brisbane and Gold Coast</span>\n        <span class=\"meta\">Roof repairs · restoration · metal roofing · gutters · inspections</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n</artifact>"}

